description: Paddy Pimblett defeated Alexander Volkov in the UFC London on Saturday night. UFC president Dana White believes Pimbleett is now a main event fighter. Pimbleatt said he deserves to be in main events and that he could sell out a stadium show with ease. The featherweight signed with the UFC last year and is one of the biggest stars in MMA outside the organization.
